ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend the course to anyone seriously interested in ancient Chinese history and with an very solid understanding of classical Chinese coming into the course.
I would recommend the class to any students who are interested in ancient Chinese intellectual history.
